cdx6500PPCTTDLCPortTable.name: cdx6500PPCTTDLCPortTable
cdx6500PPCTTDLCPortTable.description: This table contains the TDLC port configuration parameters.

cdx6500PPCTTDLCPortEntry.name: cdx6500PPCTTDLCPortEntry
cdx6500PPCTTDLCPortEntry.description: Entries in the TDLC port configuration table.

tdlcPCfgPortNumber.name: tdlcPCfgPortNumber
tdlcPCfgPortNumber.description: Port Number of the TDLC port.

tdlcPCfgPortType.name: tdlcPCfgPortType
tdlcPCfgPortType.description: Specifies the type of access protocol for this port.

tdlcPCfgPortSpeed.name: tdlcPCfgPortSpeed
tdlcPCfgPortSpeed.description: Specifies port speed in bits per second. speed300 : 300 bits per second. speed1200 : 1200 bits per second. speed2400 : 2400 bits per second. speed4800 : 4800 bits per second. speed9600 : 9600 bits per second. speed19200 : 19200 bits per second.

tdlcPCfgConnType.name: tdlcPCfgConnType
tdlcPCfgConnType.description: This specifies the control signal handshake and clocking required for a connection to be made to this port. simp - simple, no control signals required. dtr - dedicated, require the data terminal ready signal (dtr). nc - Skipped during configuration.

tdlcPCfgCRCOption.name: tdlcPCfgCRCOption
tdlcPCfgCRCOption.description: This specifies CRC checking and generation for TNPP data frames. normal - 2 Bytes Binary CRC. transp - 4 Bytes ASCII CRC. nc - Skipped during configuration.

tdlcPCfgTANControl.name: tdlcPCfgTANControl
tdlcPCfgTANControl.description: This specifies whether to accept the control characters ACK, NAK, CAN and RS in TNPP data frames. no - Not Accepted. yes - Accepted. nc - Skipped during configuration.

tdlcPCfgPagTerminalID.name: tdlcPCfgPagTerminalID
tdlcPCfgPagTerminalID.description: This specifies the identifier for the paging terminal connected.

tdlcPCfgResponseControl.name: tdlcPCfgResponseControl
tdlcPCfgResponseControl.description: This specifies whether to respond to the paging terminal when the TFRI does not have connection with TFR. yes - Will respond only when the TFRI has connection with TFR. no - Will respond irrespective of TFRI connection with TFR.

tdlcPCfgElectricalInterfaceType.name: tdlcPCfgElectricalInterfaceType
tdlcPCfgElectricalInterfaceType.description: Specify the Electrical Interface Type: V.24 - V.24 Electrical Interface Type V.35 - V.35 Electrical Interface Type V.36 - V.36 Electrical Interface Type X.21 - X.21 Electrical Interface Type NONE - Electrically disabled

tdlcPCfgV24ElectricalInterfaceOption.name: tdlcPCfgV24ElectricalInterfaceOption
tdlcPCfgV24ElectricalInterfaceOption.description: Specify the Pin 22 option: RI - V.24 uses Pin 22 for Ring Indicator output signal TM - V.24 uses Pin 22 for Test Mode input signal

tdlcPCfgHighSpeedElectricalInterfaceOpti.name: tdlcPCfgHighSpeedElectricalInterfaceOption
tdlcPCfgHighSpeedElectricalInterfaceOpti.description: Specify the cable type: NONE - V.35/V.36/X.21 DCE with straight through cable XOVER - V.35/V.36/X.21 DCE with crossover adapter cable

tdlcPGStatPortSpeed.name: tdlcPGStatPortSpeed
tdlcPGStatPortSpeed.description: This indicates port speed in bits per second.

tdlcPGStatFramingErrors.name: tdlcPGStatFramingErrors

tdlcPFSStatENQFramesOut.name: tdlcPFSStatENQFramesOut

tdlcPFSStatNAKFramesOut.name: tdlcPFSStatNAKFramesOut

tdlcPFSStatRSFramesIn.name: tdlcPFSStatRSFramesIn

tdlcPFSStatDataFramesInDiscarded.name: tdlcPFSStatDataFramesInDiscarded
